events.name: Movement Class with Setareh Fatehi
events.description:
This is an invitation for an online gathering to dance from our rooms/livingrooms/kitchens. Anyone can join with a phone or a laptop preferably on Skype.
We'll do one hour of warm up (body-balance) with Saghar Hosseinpour who will join us from Tehran and then an hour of dancing together, organised by Setareh Fatehi. If you wish to join send a Skype msg to akhtarakhtari (Setareh Fatehi Irani) or a whatsapp msg to +31625015699 (setareh's phone) the latest half an hour before we start. We'll gather at 18:45 to arrange all the technical set up to start at 19:00. We can have 9 people connecting directly to Saghar and the rest will connect through Setareh. Music will be live on http://mixlr.com/swimاو/. This needs vpn if you are joining from Iran.
